Titolo: Collar × Malice

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: Collar × Malice is a visual novel video game developed and published by Idea Factory under their Otomate brand. It was released for PlayStation Vita on August 18, 2016 in Japan, and by Aksys Games in North America and Europe on July 28, 2017. A Nintendo Switch port has also been released in 2020. The game was well received by critics, and sold well in Japan for a niche game of its genre and platform. A fan disc, Collar × Malice: Unlimited, was released on July 26, 2018. An anime adaptation has been announced.

